<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/233> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #233" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "The Tribunes of 456 were reelected (Liv. 3.31.1; Dion. Hal. 10.33.1). Dion. Hal. names Icilius (10.33.1, and 40.1); and Livy, Alienus (3.31.5; cf. Dion. Hal. 10.48.3; see 454, Aediles)." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/230> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #230" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Secured passage of the Lex Icilia de Aventino publicando (Liv. 3.31.1, and 32.7; cf. 3.44.3, and 46.2; Dion. Hal. 10.31.1-32.5; on the name, cf. 10.33.1). See Rotondi 199." .
